RF Amplifier Controller
=======================

Features :

- 6 Bands selector
- Analog Power and SWR display
- 16x2 LCD Display
- Temperature Monitor
- SWR Protection
- Overheat Protection
- ALC
- Power calibration using lookup table
- LED Operation indicators
	- STBY 
	- OPER
	- ON AIR
	- BAND 80/40/20



Update 29 Dec 2023
------------------
FWD and REF linearization table is now in FLASH to accomodate more resolution.
With drawbacks that calibration will have to rewrite the entire FLASH.

FWD power is peak hold now and decay slowly.



73 DE YB1NWP


